247
00:13:12,081 --> 00:13:15,915
Buster? The guy who thought that
the blue on the map was land?

248
00:13:16,018 --> 00:13:19,010
- He's had business classes.
- Wa-Wa-Wa-Wait.

249
00:13:19,121 --> 00:13:21,589
Eighteenth-century agrarian business.

