- Totally.

355
00:20:05,527 --> 00:20:08,724
He should've been stocking up
on those "get out of jail free" cards.

356
00:20:08,831 --> 00:20:12,995
- Good one, George Michael!
- Very good.

357
00:20:13,102 --> 00:20:16,833
<i>- Two hundred for Short Line.
- I wish you guys didn't have to go so soon.</i>

358
00:20:16,939 --> 00:20:21,205
